{"tid":1604821,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「廢話提醒」聽日注意事項","createTime":"2019-09-30T05:41:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T05:41:45.000Z","uid":229986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f5d8ecc0a3d901534c8311aa8c87e026f9d3e6d6","tid":1604821,"uid":229986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:41:45.000Z","msg":"我知道大家都十分期待聽日，非常熱情地為聽日賀國慶做準備<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過因為聽日可能會有暴徒黎搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以出發前最好做返d<span style=\"color: gold;\">個人</span>準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 定返個大目標同小目標<br />\n出發前制訂好行程非常重要， 可以有效增加效率<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定返個大目標， 然後用d小目標去達到完成大目標， 一來知自己做咩， 二來可以知進度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.  諗定走佬路線<br />\n如果d暴徒出黎搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時候交通一定會亂，甚至附近會冇車<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出發前先睇定地圖諗定點走， 到時候就唔會驚嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 小心陌生人尾隨<br />\n呢排好多陌生人鍾意跟住人返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家要小心啊。<br />\n<br />\n4. 事先出發觀察地型<br />\n無論邊個，去陌生的地方都會有d驚青， 正常的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事先行多幾轉熟悉下就唔會驚嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話唔定搵到正野， 可以帶埋朋友黎品嚐下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}